$ cmd.exe: the set command

→ Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/cmd_exe/commands/set/a[`set /a`] evaluates (simple!) mathematical expressions

→ Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/cmd_exe/commands/set/p[`set /p`] to get input from a user and assign it to an → development/environment-variable[environment variable].

sa:

  `set` is affected by whether → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/cmd_exe/command-extension[command extensions] are enabled or disabled.

  → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/cmd_exe/commands/setlocal[`setlocal`] to localize changes to an environment
  
  Other → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/cmd_exe/commands[cmd.exe commands]
